'''Grakkyn''' was a [[Alcohol/Legends|liquor]] favored by [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]] on [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]], distilled from a [[Grakkyn fruit|fruit]] or its nectar. It was an ingredient in a [[Vrortic cocktail|vrortik]] "cocktail."

